# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# Build output directories (at any level)
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/generated/

# Temporary NuGet directories (build artifacts)
**/temp_nuget/

# MSBuild Binary and Structured Log
*.binlog

# Build cache and generated files
**/*.cache
**/*.dgspec.json
**/*.g.props
**/*.g.targets
**/project.assets.json
**/project.nuget.cache
**/*.AssemblyInfo.cs
**/*.AssemblyAttributes.cs
**/*.GlobalUsings.g.cs
**/*.GeneratedMSBuildEditorConfig.editorconfig
**/*.AssemblyInfoInputs.cache
**/*.FileListAbsolute.txt
**/*.CoreCompileInputs.cache

# Build logs
**/*.log
**/pcf-push-build.log
**/SolutionPackager.log

# Internal development folders (not for public)
/SolutionKE
/src

# Include releases folder (contains managed solution packages for GitHub releases)
!releases/
!releases/**/*

# Workspace and project files (internal development)
*.code-workspace
*.cdsproj
*.sln

# Deployment scripts (may contain local paths - review before including)
**/deploy.ps1

# Exclude ALL markdown files EXCEPT README.md files
# This excludes all .md files that contain development history, plans, notes, etc.
*.md

# But include README.md files (they are public documentation)
!README.md
!**/README.md

# Note: LICENSE file is not excluded (it's not a .md file)
